tyrken som jeg h\u00e5per \u00e5 finne i l\u00f8pet av en m\u00e5neds tid."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "5dd77909c223e5970f2501915ea9f7c2f2a6df5c458808db2638d623b285ec43"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2012-07-21T18:06:40.108Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Blomsterhandler ba kundene om \u00e5 skygge banen p\u00e5 grunn av snuskutt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1341232.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JAN_2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ff9c0ca0121221b29a1f01ae88d99f134b965980.jpg?596c8898"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Itj k\u00e5m in p\u00e5 butikken! -adressa.no", "Puttet blomsterjord i munnen", "Ikke \u00f8nsket effekt", "Ringvirkninger", "Savner armstyrke"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "ff9c0ca0121221b29a1f01ae88d99f134b965980"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["k\u00e5m in", "kunder", "butikken", "unna", "dag", "snus", "slutte"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "grong"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "jan br\u00f8nseth"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1341232.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JAN_2"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "-